<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.9.8">
<l>nōṟṟēṉ palpiṟavi yuṉṉaikkāṇpatō rācaiyiṉā</l>
<l>lēṟṟē ṉippiṟappē yiṭaruṟṟaṉa ṉemperumāṉ</l>
<l>kōṟṟēṉ pāyntoḻukuṅ kuḷircōlaicūḻ vēṅkaṭavā</l>
<l>vāṟṟēṉ vantaṭaintē ṉaṭiyēṉaiyāṭ koṇṭaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have endured many births; with the one desire of seeing you,</l>
<l>I welcomed this birth. Our lord, I am one who has experienced pain.</l>
<l>You of Vēṅkaṭa encircled by cool groves where wild honey runs and drips,</l>
<l rend="indent">I, who could not bear [that],</l>
<l>Came [here and] took refuge;</l>
<l rend="indent">be gracious, receiving me, your servant, in service.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
